sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>(Gateway API / HTTPRoute)
    participant REST as HTTPServerModule<br/>(Drogon)<br/>REST port/TCP
    participant gRPC as GRPCServerModule<br/>gRPC port/TCP
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler
    participant KFS as KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    participant MM as ModelManager /<br/>ModelInstance
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>2025.4
    participant MP as MediaPipe<br/>Graph Executor
    participant LLM as LLM Calculator<br/>(Continuous Batching)
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OV: Flow 1: REST Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer
    Gateway->>REST: HTTP (plaintext)
    REST->>Handler: Drogon route dispatch
    Handler->>KFS: processInferKFSRequest()
    KFS->>MM: infer()
    MM->>OV: Execute inference
    OV-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>KFS: Result tensor
    KFS-->>Handler: Response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP response
    Gateway-->>Client: Inference result

    Note over Client,OV: Flow 2: gRPC Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>gRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (plaintext)
    gRPC->>KFS: ModelInfer()
    KFS->>MM: infer()
    MM->>OV: Execute inference
    OV-->>MM: Result
    MM-->>KFS: Result
    KFS-->>gRPC: InferResponse
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 3: OpenAI Chat Completions (Streaming)
    Client->>REST: POST /v3/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer API_KEY
    REST->>Handler: Auth validation (API key)
    Handler->>MP: MediaPipe LLM graph
    MP->>LLM: Continuous batching
    LLM->>OV: GenAI inference
    loop Streaming tokens
        OV-->>LLM: Token
        LLM-->>MP: Token
        MP-->>REST: SSE event
        REST-->>Client: data: {token}<br/>HTTP SSE stream
    end
    REST-->>Client: data: [DONE]

    Note over MM,HF: Flow 4: Model Loading
    MM->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials
    S3-->>MM: Model files
    MM->>OV: Load model into runtime
    Note right of MM: Or from GCS/Azure/HuggingFace
    MM->>HF: Pull model<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>HF_TOKEN (optional)
    HF-->>MM: Model artifacts
